{"tid":307312,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港最強跌打師傅/醫生","createTime":"2017-07-03T09:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T09:05:50.000Z","uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a3822804770013969a57236e5d117db0d7f19faf","tid":307312,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T09:13:26.000Z","msg":"小妹早半年前隻右手(前臂)成日都會無啦啦痛<br />\n有時又會無啦啦痺左成分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁就當然去睇醫生啦<br />\n反正公司有得claim, 咩物理治療呀(又電又針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )都做過8,9次, 仍然無用<br />\n<br />\n跌打都有睇過, 係咁捽捽捽但都無成果<br />\n<br />\n後來再去照MRI<br />\n醫生話係右手有塊骨有小小裂左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n印象中就無整親, 跌親...唔知做咩會裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果舊好似叫三角骨<br />\n裂左好小好小<br />\n但旋轉隻手果d 動作係小小都已經會好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後醫生又話呢舊骨只會痛, 唔會令到隻手痺<br />\n可能關條頸事.....<br />\n<br />\n咁又照多次MRI 同做神經線傳導測試<br />\n只係咩追間盤有好少好少咁突出<br />\n醫生話根本好普通好正常<br />\n所以根本唔知痺既來源係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以上黎睇下有無巴絲都試過整親呢個位<br />\n想問下識唔識咩醫生有好介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5038148448365973f3db74ebe4fce5bd96278373","tid":307312,"uid":58614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T09:56:59.000Z","msg":"留名  我隻手腕位痛佐2個月都冇好轉 睇佐N次鐵打同西醫 醫生話唔洗照  轉介我8月去物理治療 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f93aab68b36cd329038159d6fe997c3a214b47a","tid":307312,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci